# Personal Training Client Tracker

## Purpose

This tracker is designed to help identify real-life patterns affecting weight loss, training consistency, energy, recovery and resilience.

Do not worry about bad days, we all have them, the point of getting really real on the answers is that ChatGPT in it’s analysis for you, may help you to see why, and be able to suggest how you can optimise things to help support your goals. 

The aim is to notice what is actually happening across the week, including training, steps, sleep disruption, energy, symptoms, food consistency, stress, parenting load, illness and period or pre-bleed patterns.

---

## How To Use This Tracker

This tracker is designed to be quick. You do not need to fill everything in at the same time, as it will auto save as you go. 

You could answer the sleep questions in the morning and do the rest in the evening, or fill in bits as they day goes on, if you don’t want to forget anything, 

Weekly measurements only need to be completed once per week, ideally on the same day each week and under similar conditions.

For example:

- same day of the week
- similar time of day
- before food where possible
- similar clothing
- same scales and measuring tape

Remember that measurements can be influenced by water retention, bloating etc. The point of doing all of this is to try to notice patterns over time. 

