## Period / Pre-Bleed Pattern Insights

Once enough data exists, look for patterns around logged period days.

Show:

- Period days logged
- Whether there appear to be changes in the 7–14 days before period days
- Whether food consistency changes before period days
- Whether usable energy changes before period days
- Whether symptoms increase before period days
- Whether steps or training reduce before period days
- Whether Whoop strain changes before period days
- Whether weight temporarily increases before period days

Use the wording “pre-bleed window” rather than “luteal phase”, because the client is on the pill.

